        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Building Our Opportunities to Survive and Thrive Act of 2021 or the BOOST Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill allows certain individual taxpayers a refundable income-based tax credit equal to $3,000 in a taxable year. It also directs the Internal Revenue Service to establish a program for making advance payments of such credit on a monthly basis.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
